        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Hatné - Skala a Hrádok "
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nNáš spolupracovník Tomáš Humaj vytvoril novú skvelú kresbu hradiska. Tentokrát sme &nbsp;trochu povolili uzdu fantázii a nakreslil mierne romantickú predstavu oboch <a href=\"http://www.hradiska.sk/search/label/Hatn%C3%A9\" target=\"_blank\">hrádkov v obci Hatné</a>, založenú sčasti na aktuálnej situácii a sčasti na základe zachovalej povesti. Podľa tejto povesti, ktorá bola zaznamenaná už koncom 19. a opäť ju spomína Štefan Janšák v 30. rokoch 20. storočia, boli oba hrádky spojené koženým mostom. V skutočnosti &nbsp;sa zatiaľ archeologicky nepotvrdilo, že by oba hrádky boli osídlené súčasne, tobôž nie existencia koženého mosta, ale čo ak ...&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjdruD456JSr7yr6KauuGuU9SSWdlOI5pBRl7areyaupetStkIB8qv1GMmd0BEWmueB-WI-9AjkeUUjY4X5pU0QFPnSakEWHT9rhatJvy2l_jTrNdv0sONgOMZOIUsVrZz8FquUx4cf3oY/s1600/P6172214.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"226\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjdruD456JSr7yr6KauuGuU9SSWdlOI5pBRl7areyaupetStkIB8qv1GMmd0BEWmueB-WI-9AjkeUUjY4X5pU0QFPnSakEWHT9rhatJvy2l_jTrNdv0sONgOMZOIUsVrZz8FquUx4cf3oY/s320/P6172214.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\">Kresba sa nazýva&nbsp;<b>Návrat miestneho vladyku z boja</b></td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh72hoem-k2JkFPHnvk6r5jNkmloCto6EnqfWoaKxoHk4cpVs1fTPJsTmGkKytp26bE9nvdm10z0wLQRfboCb7tilAAjlrovXZsy98Q5zXwhX6GkXzj2wH2_WvqKFbi_Xu55mlgL63s9dE/s1600/P6172217.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh72hoem-k2JkFPHnvk6r5jNkmloCto6EnqfWoaKxoHk4cpVs1fTPJsTmGkKytp26bE9nvdm10z0wLQRfboCb7tilAAjlrovXZsy98Q5zXwhX6GkXzj2wH2_WvqKFbi_Xu55mlgL63s9dE/s320/P6172217.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEggoIfcXvK6hp659Nz0_7nbj4R59Jas5igRyE_lxjMvQcvzj7sGoSE-H-UqWQ4m_uIhPPnV-uxXg10FN8bmd_rV8KVWUKuRkiD4zGqPz8msYrnd0perDQuTQ-ek3wtOwk6jHYg-GxfE1Fk/s1600/P6172219.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEggoIfcXvK6hp659Nz0_7nbj4R59Jas5igRyE_lxjMvQcvzj7sGoSE-H-UqWQ4m_uIhPPnV-uxXg10FN8bmd_rV8KVWUKuRkiD4zGqPz8msYrnd0perDQuTQ-ek3wtOwk6jHYg-GxfE1Fk/s320/P6172219.JPG\" width=\"263\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5Ecm1Z2gRPyv3agmWTcWr5dl0UF8B0V4u4wSmCLQwy1K_mTJNdCBes3YTfxwlftmY_X9t4nBWLg9A9vagt5kzZdAbvQiBx9X95TshCU8jO4ktWlrWiD3vdxaCG6NnqeVsysd9foLESbc/s1600/P6172221.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5Ecm1Z2gRPyv3agmWTcWr5dl0UF8B0V4u4wSmCLQwy1K_mTJNdCBes3YTfxwlftmY_X9t4nBWLg9A9vagt5kzZdAbvQiBx9X95TshCU8jO4ktWlrWiD3vdxaCG6NnqeVsysd9foLESbc/s320/P6172221.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjJyH-qi6hPs0W4MiiS8M1sPL2V3umwWYZ1T93NE2hP6XdoFCDIGfW9WXsp4DQejypE5zbB7oJjbCDTLY8BnElAEuMzSH2Kjdlm9cCE6Ke8T98vphf0JrIytUfUpaTOOu9SX8GbfA8QOqI/s1600/P6172222.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjJyH-qi6hPs0W4MiiS8M1sPL2V3umwWYZ1T93NE2hP6XdoFCDIGfW9WXsp4DQejypE5zbB7oJjbCDTLY8BnElAEuMzSH2Kjdlm9cCE6Ke8T98vphf0JrIytUfUpaTOOu9SX8GbfA8QOqI/s320/P6172222.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhdMrRlUmW6d7vIO0w2bb_IrgsD0dkdfssyiid8ii_qWkKs34-SUiesqXy5wvkA91R3qMHAl6h_dS3DjzEKfGkcAtFbwdDD9lfblJzfMPkGMwqHXFtL_nq7M1EQ4PUee_g2o_eUUsACLFs/s1600/P6172226.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"227\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhdMrRlUmW6d7vIO0w2bb_IrgsD0dkdfssyiid8ii_qWkKs34-SUiesqXy5wvkA91R3qMHAl6h_dS3DjzEKfGkcAtFbwdDD9lfblJzfMPkGMwqHXFtL_nq7M1EQ4PUee_g2o_eUUsACLFs/s320/P6172226.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh_2Rba97tXo7tyTWWLB5dindyfjuoyIu4BCBo7J2ofHnSxUC5C12jW9bs2xwkucU5FZCusAQcvOJsoRt06aReIutPWC9mAYLXYb5moThYZ2EIcY481i4aFopKF2TYRatwiUIGWejbWMIc/s1600/P6172228.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh_2Rba97tXo7tyTWWLB5dindyfjuoyIu4BCBo7J2ofHnSxUC5C12jW9bs2xwkucU5FZCusAQcvOJsoRt06aReIutPWC9mAYLXYb5moThYZ2EIcY481i4aFopKF2TYRatwiUIGWejbWMIc/s320/P6172228.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEicC07GVzxN58hh0RepLWBKq_4Hn76dVWtjLT34ddYx4EO9gDyh_kirnCBZy_0gRnJs62j9J92qLvHSjzt2FyLBXAx-xvBJo_BdJWY5fkySvrG454GhKN241HX6SIF6vTcD_2zKCfZz4dQ/s1600/P6172231.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEicC07GVzxN58hh0RepLWBKq_4Hn76dVWtjLT34ddYx4EO9gDyh_kirnCBZy_0gRnJs62j9J92qLvHSjzt2FyLBXAx-xvBJo_BdJWY5fkySvrG454GhKN241HX6SIF6vTcD_2zKCfZz4dQ/s320/P6172231.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nVal hrádku na Skale bol zrejme o niečo nižší ako na obrázku a signálne vežičky nie sú zatiaľ archeologicky potvrdené. Ostatné časti &nbsp;kresby však vychádzajú z našich dostupných znalostí o tvare a pôdoryse oboch hradísk v minulosti, o spôsobe budovania domov a konštrukcií drevených palisád v časoch Veľkej Moravy. Taktiež vzhľad, výstroj a výzbroj družiny je možné zaradiť do obdobia 9. storočia.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nVďaka za skvelý počin. Obrázok bude súčasťou informačnej tabule, ktorú naše Občianske združenie Hradiská umiestni pri hradisku v Hatnom v budúcnosti.</div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhVXOS3Eq3cyw9U99PyCBQeBntQXYWxhtge8yJr01evOOEKwV46Q2HZzrZOBcaK49p2eSfBXifoMytQVsVSIhiB8_bU6jt2jiTis1EiTc3nmF4cHo0xZdqSLI7Ery7vGTLPigWqN_xkTi0/s1600/Hlavic%25CC%258Cka+web-stra%25CC%2581nky_2.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"95\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhVXOS3Eq3cyw9U99PyCBQeBntQXYWxhtge8yJr01evOOEKwV46Q2HZzrZOBcaK49p2eSfBXifoMytQVsVSIhiB8_bU6jt2jiTis1EiTc3nmF4cHo0xZdqSLI7Ery7vGTLPigWqN_xkTi0/s320/Hlavic%25CC%258Cka+web-stra%25CC%2581nky_2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />"
